@startuml
title ObjectStorageBucket Formal Lifecycle

[*] --> Observed
Observed --> Retryable : CREATING, UPDATING, RESOLVING
Observed --> Active : READY
Observed --> Failed : FAILED, DELETED
Active --> DeletePending : delete requested
Retryable --> DeletePending : delete requested
Failed --> DeletePending : delete requested
DeletePending --> Deleted : finalizer removed after delete

state Retryable
state Active
state Failed
state DeletePending
state Deleted
@enduml
